

**Matsh g Jesus ab haꞌi i ha wai mat ab si wecho wo e mashchamad **

*An g neid g Matthew 4:18-22; Mark 1:16-20 *

1 Sh am hu hebai g Jesus an kehk mo an i koa hegai al kahchki mo hab chehgig Galilee Kahchki. Kutsh g hemajkam ab wabsh i shodbinidahi s‑kaimkch g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. 2 Sh neid mo gohk wapalko am wupulshpi shuhdagi ch ed. Tsh g enigakam am ha dagito k ged hu ha wapkon g e‑chuchagia. 3 Kutsh am i chesh g Jesus hema ha eda idam wapalko. Sh heg d Simon eniga. Sh hab ahg matsh am wo shaꞌi nuꞌichkwua shuhdagi ch ed. Tsh g Simon hab juh. Tsh ab i dahiwua g Jesus wahlko ch ed k am ha mashcha g hemajkam. 

4 Tsh am i haꞌasa haꞌichu ha ahgid k hab ahg ihda Simon mat am wo i himch g e‑wahlko mo am s‑juhk g shuhdagi k am wo i huduni g e‑chuchagia ha wehm g e‑wehm chikpandam. 

5 Sh hab kaij g Simon, “T‑mashchamdam, ge att chuhug shaꞌi si chikpan k pi haꞌichu shaꞌi bei. P wabshaba am t‑ahgid matt am ep wo i huduni g t‑chuchagia. Pegih, tt am hab wo t‑juh.” 6 Kutsh wa woho am hihim k am i ha huhuds ge e‑chuchagia k atsh shaꞌi si muꞌi waptopi ha ui matsh chum alo e wanikumia g ha‑chuchagia. 

7 Kush am haꞌi ep chikpan hema wahlko ch ed. Kumtsh idam ab hahawa si ha wai mat am wo i ha wehmt. Tsh wa woho ab i himch g e‑wahlko k wehs ha shuhshud g waptopikaj mat chum alo wachkk g ha‑wapalko. 

8 Tsh am i nei g Simon mat haschu has i e juh k ab si i gei g e‑tohtonkaj Jesus wui k hab wabsh kaij, “Ih, dani wabsh pi apꞌekam oꞌodham. K pi hab chum mahs maps wo ni‑wehmajk ahpi s‑apꞌekam ni‑kownalig.” 9 Kutsh wehsijj hegam mash wehmaj si e totods neidch mat has e juh. 10 Haꞌi hegam wehmaj chikpandam g Peter ash d James ch John ch ash d aꞌalidaj hegai mash hab chehgig Zebedee. 

Sh g Jesus hab kaij ab Simon wui, “Pi g am shaꞌi has e tahtkkad. Iꞌajed apt imhab g oꞌodham an wo ha uꞌud ni‑wehhejed.” 11 Tsh am wabsh i chum ai g shuhdagi koa idam k am i ha wuwhas g wapalko k wehs haꞌichu am wabsh i dagito k gm hu i oi g Jesus. 

**Matsh g Jesus hema doaj mash g chuhkugaj wabsh muhkhim **

*An g neid g Matthew 8:1-4; Mark 1:40-45 *

12 Sh am hu hebai g Jesus am hasko kihhim ch ed oimmed. Kush am hema g oꞌodham wehsko maꞌishch hegai mumkidag mo g chuhkugaj muhkhim. Tsh am jiwia g Jesus. Kutsh heg am i chehg k ab si kupal i gei wui k hab kaij, “Ab g si i s‑ni‑hoꞌigeꞌid k i ni‑doajid pej maptp wo tatchuad.” 

13 Tsh g Jesus ab tahtam k hab kaij, “Am o wa s‑apꞌe. Doajini.” Tsh am ha hekaj i doa. 

14 Tsh g Jesus ab chehani k hab kaij, “Pi g am hedai ahgid ab amjed ihda k wabshaba am ha hekaj wo hih pahl wui. T am wo m‑chechga k wo wohokamch mapt doa. Pt am hab haha wo juh hegai iagchulida mo wa g Jiosh em‑chehani Mosesbad oꞌohana ed. T hab wo s‑mahchk g hemajkam mapt woho doa.” 

15 Tsh amjed gam hu hih hegai oꞌodham. Kutsh wehsko i e ahgahi ihda matsh g Jesus hab juh. Tsh hekaj muꞌi hemajkam am wui hihi mat wo kah g haꞌichu ahgaj k wo e dodaj. 16 Tsh g Jesus am wo ha mihshmad k wo ha dodajid k amjed gam hu hejelko wo him k wo e hoꞌigeꞌidahu. 

**Matsh g Jesus hema doaj mo ab wabsh i s‑moik **

*An g neid g Matthew 9:1-8; Mark 2:1-12 *

17 Sh am hu hebai ehp mash g Jesus am ha mashcham. Sh am haꞌi dadha g chehanig ha mashchamdam ch hegam mo si oid g chehanig ch hab e aꞌaga Palasi. Idam atsh ga hu aꞌaijed am dada ab amjed g Galilee chekshani ch Judea chekshani ch ab Jerusalem kihhim t amjed. Tsh g Jiosh ab si mah g gewkdag g Jesus mat wo ha dodaj g kokꞌodam. 

18 Tsh am haꞌi dada g chechoj hema uꞌadch g pi himidkam. Id ash ab wabsh i s‑moik ch am woꞌo e‑wahkus ed. 19 Kush am i chum s‑wahkidamk kih ch ed matsh wo chehgi g Jesus ab si hiwigch mat wo doaj. Sh wabshaba shaꞌi si s‑hemajkamag. Kutsh pi has masma am hu wo i e wahki. Tsh heg hekaj gan hu hahawa i cheshaj kih dahm k am ge maggad g kih maꞌishpadag k amjed ab i huduni g woꞌikudaj am ha shahgid g hemajkam k am woi mash am kehk g Jesus. 

20 Tsh am i nei g Jesus moki ab si hiwig idam k hab kaij ab wui ihda oꞌodham, “Ni‑nawoj, ab ani s‑m‑hoꞌigeꞌid ch gam hu hab i juh g pi ap m‑chuꞌijig.” 

21 Kush hegam chehanig ha mashchamdam ch Palasi wabsh hejel hab e ahg, “Ih, shaꞌi si pi ap neok ihda oꞌodham hab masma e wepogidch g Jiosh. Heg at waꞌi Jiosh wo e nako mat gam hu hab wo i juh g pi ap ha‑chuꞌijig.” 

22 Sh g Jesus s‑mahch mo haschu am oidahim ch hab kaij ab ha wui, “Pi g am wo shaꞌi oidahim manis pi woho edgid g gewkdag mant gam hu hab wo i juh g pi ap ha‑chuꞌijig. 23 Bam elid mo s‑pehegim hab e kaij mat gam hu hab i e juh g pi ap chuꞌijigaj no ge hedai s‑mahch mas s‑wohom hab e juh. 24 Pegih, nt wo em‑chehgi mani woho ge gewkdag ch hab wua mani has i kaij ahni Jiosh si Kehsha.” Neh, bash kaij ch hab hahawa kaij heg wui pi himidkam, “I g wamig k am behꞌi g e‑wahkus k hihm am uhpam.” 

25 Tsh am ha hekaj i wami hegai oꞌodham k am bei g e‑wahkus k gam hu uhpam hih ab si ihmch g Jiosh. 26 Tsh g hemajkam si has i elid k ab ihm g Jiosh hab kaijch, “Shaꞌi si s‑kehg haꞌichu ach neid id tashkaj.” 

**Matsh g Jesus ab i wai g Levibad \(Matthew\) **

*An g neid g Matthew 9:9-13; Mark 2:13-17 *

27 Sh hema d lial kowlantdam g kownal wehhejed ch hab chehgig Levi. Tsh g Jesus am cheh. Kush am daha heg eda kih mo am chikpan. 

Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Oi g i ni‑oid.” 28 Tsh g Levi am ha hekaj i wuhshani k am wabsh i dagito wehs haꞌichu k gam hu i oi. 

29-30 Am waꞌi mia amjed, tsh g Levi am hab juh g geꞌe gegosig am wehhejed g Jesus. Sh am haꞌi oiopo g Palasi mash idam haꞌi d chehanig ha mashchamdam. Sh eda muꞌijj hegam mash am ha wehm e gegosid d lial kowlantdam hab masma mo g Levi. 

Kush hegam Palasi am ha neid ch hekaj s‑ha kehꞌid g Jesus chuhchai hab ha ahgch, “Ih, shahchu am ahgch am ha wehm e gegosid idam pi ap hemajkam, chum hems am ha wehm g lial kowlantdam?” 

31 Sh g Jesus hab kaij ab ha wui, “Idam pi ap hemajkam o s‑e doꞌibiamk hab masma mat g kokꞌodam wo s‑e doajidam. Hegam mo hab e elid mo s‑apꞌe at pi wo tatchua g mahkai. 32 Pi ant hab ahgk ia jiwia manis wo ha doꞌibia hegam mo pi e doꞌibiamk.” 

**Ha‑himdag mash heꞌekkio pi e gegosid **

*An g neid g Matthew 9:14-17; Mark 2:18-22 *

33 Sh haꞌi g hemajkam hab kaij ab wui g Jesus, “Neh, muꞌikko o pi e gegosid ch wabsh e hoꞌigeꞌidahun hegam mo ab wecho e mashcham g John ch hegam mo ab ha wecho e mashcham g Palasi. Kuki wabshaba ahpi g m‑wohochuddam pi hab e wua.” 

34 Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Nat hig pi wo e gegos g wo ha hohntam naipijju mat eda heg am wo ha wehmajk? 35 T am wo i e ai mat pi am hu wo ha wehmajk. T am hahawa pi wo e gegos. Pegih, bat wo wa e juh idam ni‑naipijju mant hekid pi ia hu wo ha wehmajk.” 

36 Sh am hahawa chum ha tashogid g Jesus mat g mashchamaj pi ap wo wehnad g ha‑himdag ash hab kaij, “Pi at hedai g wechij ikuskaj wo shohsho g hekiuchij lihwa mat wo s‑e wia nat pi wo i dahiwua k baꞌich wo i wantsh g hekiuchij. T hab waꞌap pi wo apꞌet g hekiuchij nat ge wo wepo mahsk g wechij ikus. 37 T pi hedai g wechij nawait am wo toa hekiuchij haꞌichu elidag kokstal ch ed. Tp hab wo sha e juh, t g wechij nawait wo wantsh g haꞌichu elidag. T g nawait wo iawua k g haꞌichu elidag wo e padch. 38 Neh, hemho wa at g wechij nawait am wo e toa wechij haꞌichu elidag kokstal ch ed. 

39 “Pi o hedai tatchua mat wo ih g wechij nawait hekid ab i jehkiok g hekiuchij nawait nat pi hab wo chei mo baꞌich i s‑ap hab kahk g hekiuchij.” 

